<plot>Three tech-savvy 8th-grade girls try to help their friend who's been cyber bullied. When popular girl, Skye receives threatening emails, text messages and voice-mails, her best friend Melody asks classmate Adina for help. When Adina says yes, her best friend Clara is confused. Skye is stuck up and has never been nice to them in the past. So why is Adina helping her? While solving the mystery, the girls learn about more than just the bully's identity - they learn about friendship and growing up in the digital age of technology.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?023599</url></doc>
